{"tid":389903,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[冷戰時代] 英國民眾應立即準備應對核攻擊","createTime":"2017-09-06T15:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T09:44:22.000Z","uid":89046,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b8d174cb439a6224fb8f6c56adca6e0362ae4f5","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m6U9T3R3EQg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm6U9T3R3EQg&d=HaY5XNuWdZBOgaSlRii9WTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9bc12ab0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m6U9T3R3EQg</a><br />\n<br />\n70年代英國國防部宣傳片 當預計英國本土48小時內將受到核攻擊就會作全國緊急廣播 於7、80年代片段屬機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n段片首先講核爆會帶嚟熱力、衝擊波同輻射塵，跟住講到防空警報已經開始不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後講要留喺屋企唔好周圍走，要點樣去揀一處最安全嘅地方整個 &quot;inner refuge&quot;，舖滿雜物堆泥堆沙包隔輻射，然後匿喺入面14日，預左會冇水冇電冇人救你，周圍又有火災同致命輻射危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以要預備定一大堆食物、水同其他野，教埋你點全面節省資源，連緊急屎塔都教埋你點整，真係世界級，不過越睇就越覺得絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後講到死左人點處理，睇完成套嘢心諗黐撚線邊有可能到最後仲生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，就算生存到 到時不如死左去就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b81b1031b74fbf57649f126049424141943f77","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/de/ProtectAndSurvive.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fd%2Fde%2FProtectAndSurvive.jpg&h=4f34e257&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64d096d8adb56ec5cf7c81c97c59c5cc0cd62c1f","tid":389903,"uid":109050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:51:47.000Z","msg":"依家睇返以前D片覺得好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8d77d2f23ea1236c9d2177d54e13317ee9d1c6","tid":389903,"uid":12440,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:04:09.000Z","msg":"明明冇乜時間 啲過場整咁長做乜鳩"},{"pid":"8d62d6df35d7f0894302c04bfe5080da7cd9f500","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明冇乜時間 啲過場整咁長做乜鳩</blockquote><br />\n就喺要整啲令人不安嘅過場動畫<br />\n啲市民先會保持住危機意識 (鳩估)"},{"pid":"f6f9d52c2b49621ef43b4bdf198ff059d61928f4","tid":389903,"uid":28654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ba06f03c97ab1d84303440632742fae9719f52","tid":389903,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T18:02:24.000Z","msg":"有冇update版"},{"pid":"942a920cf01b28bb213f5acf834f50707c6ad4d6","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇update版</blockquote><br />\n廣告就應該冇 但喺印刷版近年有reprinted version 內容應該同40年前一樣<br />\nImperial War Museum賣緊7鎊一本<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.iwmshop.org.uk/product/25921/Protect_and_Survive\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iwmshop.org.uk%2Fproduct%2F25921%2FProtect_and_Survive&d=HaY5XNuWdZBOgaSlRii9WTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=cc169ba7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.iwmshop.org.uk/product/25921/Protect_and_Survive</a><br />\n<br />\n當然就咁上網search 都會搵到開心版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://digitalarchive.wilsoncenter.org/document/110193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdigitalarchive.wilsoncenter.org%2Fdocument%2F110193&d=HaY5XNuWdZBOgaSlRii9WTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=be715c36\" target=\"_blank\">http://digitalarchive.wilsoncenter.org/document/110193</a>"},{"pid":"bf39c2f8ce62a7a0f70dbde1ff5c099b6cfa5e2b","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e9e1b8d7b1c289f196daf4f20f127b4a3c2690","tid":389903,"uid":28654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21941f64c42b14577d733d1cd1f8988d3350f704","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T20:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.atomica.co.uk/home.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.atomica.co.uk%2Fhome.gif&h=aeab20f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d41a1dccc53772e4d449fc0928607b35dc5d23","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T01:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c90be419c904d538e2cf0515681e0ccd7ff4c5","tid":389903,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T02:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b4634179124376af1e6371059f95392f04b80d","tid":389903,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T07:19:40.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f22b15063e55d68995dc999ea3faf67ea9d6ca64","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4bfc2b6243e8aa0cd4e765c386ba9314b85e49","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T00:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919f16eb9f22ea5f23a443aaea1e044cbf1d46e5","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T09:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a2ee9aee963f1b973bfcf6ee0defdc23dfa576","tid":389903,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T14:35:06.000Z","msg":"救命"},{"pid":"6f6db6149b75a24234bf0e8607b79e08f04ee73f","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>救命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Stay in your refuge</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nThe dangers will be so intense that you may all need to stay inside your inner refuge in the fall-out room for at least forty-eight hours. If you need to go to the lavatory, or to replenish food or water supplies, do not stay outside your refuge for a second longer than is necessary.&nbsp;<br />\nAfter forty-eight hours the danger from fall-out will lessen but you could still be risking your life by exposure to it. The longer you spend in your refuge the better. Listen to your radio.&nbsp;<br />\n<strong>DO NOT GO OUTSIDE until the radio tells you it is safe to do so.</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a95bc114f1f267e1b95d45a566e81afe0f059bd","tid":389903,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:47:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  留名陣間睇"},{"pid":"811ed18b97eadb0a48354ce90943a60698d8ff3d","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32faa9ce812ec710261cb507297c9c7f1509fcc","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3866ac131c51cfd00dd24f09125e437b05fbda","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f012003b063f5ab9129a985b36d0f5c9a5f0344","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cc5a2e69a42624146bd69cd299482c367512a8","tid":389903,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}